      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774706708,
      "updated": 1774706708
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7e0130000000000c00c25",
      "text": "from [2026/01/25]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774706708,
      "updated": 1774706708
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7e0130000000000c00c26",
      "text": "謎解き2026-01-25",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774706708,
      "updated": 1774706708
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7e0130000000000c00c27",
      "text": "#Shiroikaibutsu",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774706708,
      "updated": 1774706708
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7e0130000000000c00c28",
      "text": ">[Shiroikaibutsu_ https://x.com/Shiroikaibutsu_/status/2014861578345316698] note謎「行方」のクイズを作りました",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774706708,
      "updated": 1774706708
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7e0130000000000c00c29",
      "text": "> いなくなった友人からの手紙がとどいたようだけど…",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774706708,
      "updated": 1774706708
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7e0130000000000c00c2a",
      "text": "> 今回は2つの謎が隠れているみたい。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774706708,
      "updated": 1774706708
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7e0130000000000c00c2b",
      "text": "> [https://pbs.twimg.com/media/G_Y5i1aWgAAoqZd?format=jpg&name=large#.png]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774706708,
      "updated": 1774706708
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7e0130000000000c00c2c",
      "text": "\t下に書いてるのの解読はできたんだけど、2つ目の謎って何？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774706708,
      "updated": 1774706708
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7e0130000000000c00c2d",
      "text": "\t\t[~ 漢字の隠されてないとこだけ読むと「たすけてよ」]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774706708,
      "updated": 1774706708
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7e0130000000000c00c2e",
      "text": "\t[~ 文字に色がついてるのは意味がありそう]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774706708,
      "updated": 1774706708
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7e0130000000000c00c2f",
      "text": "\t\t[~ 白夜！ 赤歌？？？？←いまここ]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774706708,
      "updated": 1774706708
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7e0130000000000c00c30",
      "text": "\t最初黒いところに何かあるかと思った[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774706708,
      "updated": 1774706708
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7e0130000000000c00c31",
      "text": "\t [~ なかったので色をぶつくさ独り言言ってたらできた]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774706708,
      "updated": 1774706708
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7e0130000000000c00c32",
      "text": "\t 　うわー、なるほど、そういうことか[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774706708,
      "updated": 1774706708
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7e0130000000000c00c33",
      "text": "\t 　　理解した、うまいことつくってあるなぁ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774706708,
      "updated": 1774706708
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7e0130000000000c00c34",
      "text": "\t[~ わかったと思うけどそれが原因なら友人を助けられそうにはない][yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774706708,
      "updated": 1774706708
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7e0130000000000c00c35",
      "text": "\t [~ 手紙の内容からは何か読解できないのだろうか]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1774706708,
      "updated": 1774706708
    },
    {
      "id": "69c7e0130000000000c00c36",
